parameters.name: q
parameters.description: string Full-text search query string.

parameters.name: Optional
parameters.description: Parameters

parameters.name: download
parameters.description:
string Restrict to volumes by download availability.

Acceptable values are: " epub " - All volumes with epub.

parameters.name: filter
parameters.description:
string Filter search results.

Acceptable values are: " ebooks " - All Google eBooks.
" free-ebooks " - Google eBook with full volume text viewability.
" full " - Public can view entire volume text.
" paid-ebooks " - Google eBook with a price.
" partial " - Public able to see parts of text.

parameters.name: langRestrict
parameters.description: string Restrict results to books with this language code.

parameters.name: libraryRestrict
parameters.description:
string Restrict search to this user's library.

Acceptable values are: " my-library " - Restrict to the user's library, any shelf.
" no-restrict " - Do not restrict based on user's library.

parameters.name: maxResults
parameters.description: unsigned integer Maximum number of results to return. Acceptable values are 0 to 40 , inclusive.

parameters.name: orderBy
parameters.description:
string Sort search results.

Acceptable values are: " newest " - Most recently published.
" relevance " - Relevance to search terms.

parameters.name: partner
parameters.description: string Restrict and brand results for partner ID.

parameters.name: printType
parameters.description:
string Restrict to books or magazines.

Acceptable values are: " all " - All volume content types.
" books " - Just books.
" magazines " - Just magazines.

parameters.name: projection
parameters.description:
string Restrict information returned to a set of selected fields.

Acceptable values are: " full " - Includes all volume data.
" lite " - Includes a subset of fields in volumeInfo and accessInfo.

parameters.name: showPreorders
parameters.description: boolean Set to true to show books available for preorder. Defaults to false.

parameters.name: source
parameters.description: string String to identify the originator of this request.

parameters.name: startIndex
parameters.description: unsigned integer Index of the first result to return (starts at 0)
